{"tid":1071131,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Marvel主題遊樂設施 宣萱飾演神盾局科技館工程師","createTime":"2019-03-21T06:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T10:53:05.000Z","uid":109809,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bb8d19f292579535eacd10ad38e48fba1301beb6","tid":1071131,"uid":109809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"香港迪士尼樂園最新Marvel主題遊樂設施「蟻俠與黃蜂女：擊戰特攻！」將於3月28日舉行揭幕儀式！<br />\n<br />\n「蟻俠」Paul Rudd、Marvel Studios 主席 Kevin Feige 同《蟻俠》及《蟻俠2: 黃蜂女現身》導演Peyton Reed 都會親身嚟到香港，同設施中原創嘅全新Marvel角色&mdash;神盾局科技館總工程師林樂詩Leslie（由宣萱飾演）一齊擔任主禮嘉賓<br />\n<br />\n喺全新遊樂設施入面，賓客將同蟻俠及黃蜂女一齊響應鐵甲奇俠嘅號召，抵禦邪惡勢力Hydra喺香港發動嘅襲擊，擊敗Arnim Zola同佢嘅機械蟲大軍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w310b2s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw310b2s.jpg&h=3043b7a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n留名睇佢比敵人綁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e94a5160b29189a6552f4f5e4fcb3f5fa8d8883","tid":1071131,"uid":12782,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:46:09.000Z","msg":"見到你句「留名睇俾人綁架」笑咗"},{"pid":"0d26c3fb480a06a7e958bfc7215e29255ce7d69c","tid":1071131,"uid":52423,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:49:12.000Z","msg":"搵佢做明日戰記劉嘉玲個角色順眼好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf7e8c05732db29769c909f8b4ccd078e6a102a","tid":1071131,"uid":58867,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:51:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9MIb6tYC0A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9MIb6tYC0A8&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3NqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=abb393f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9MIb6tYC0A8</a>"},{"pid":"cb5f04127bc37a7fc790498dc3f524d4c0ae885a","tid":1071131,"uid":145043,"like":0,"dislike":